name: axios
text:
Gov. Gretchen Whitmer slammed President Trump this evening for endangering her with his rhetoric after he responded to "lock her up" chants at a rally in Muskegon, Michigan, by saying "lock 'em all up" 
https://t.co/BWj01OylmY

name: axios
text:
NEW: New Zealand's top health official said today after reporting the first community COVID-19 case for 12 days, a man who worked on ships, that it "shows our systems ... are working" and "the risk of onward transmission is contained"

text:
